"Optional \"here-and-now\" terms (current location name, on-scene "
"character names). A chunk whose text mentions any of them gets a small "
"additive boost so memories about the current scene surface more readily. "
"No effect when omitted."
msgstr ""

#: axiom.memory.VectorMemory.query:7 of
msgid "Restrict the search to chunks of this type (e.g. \"lore\")."
msgstr ""

#: axiom.memory.VectorMemory.query:8 of
