"Exclude chunks of this type (e.g. the narrative query passes \"lore\" so "
"lore entries never eat its k budget)."
msgstr ""

#: axiom.memory.VectorMemory.query:11 of
msgid ""
"Each returned candidate carries ``entry_id`` (the chunk's source id when "
"one was stored, e.g. a lore entry's id; otherwise ``None``)."
